Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GIGOLO (DOCHINIPIRA)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are a lot of pretty girls out today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Kaito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been at school at all lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried and was wondering what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't be back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A part-time gig?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My actual job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actual job?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a seduction artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a woman this morning who gave me 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to waste chatting with campus friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to seduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw a strict boundary between work and school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's okay to break the rules sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea... it would feel this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a professional seducer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to take advantage of beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked you, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be the perfect type to take my virginity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't have a chance until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A professional must stick to his policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I sounded too cheesy back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucker, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've double-crossed us for the last time, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fucking dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with the Hazakura gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want the gang to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you rather join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you join, we can forget about our differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to work alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't join a ga-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll teach you to talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asswipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which gang are you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in any gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the fuck you think you are, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Suzuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is a friend of our boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll overlook this incident today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to have a talk with that gigolo over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to lecture me, save you breath, Suzuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can survive out there forever as a lone wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone against all the gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My rank and position are different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me just because you're more experienced!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep acting tough, that pretty face of yours will get smashed eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for the newsflash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucking gigolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to tell you that besides Hazakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are plenty of other gangs swarming around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you make your mark and fit in somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be in trouble with all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scare tactics won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll con enough women to get back at you in time, Suzuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the Porsche you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me anywhere you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! What happening to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "yo" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been gone for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been pimping again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like you're my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about my lifestyle when you decided to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe your half of the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, I kinda lost it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll make it up to you in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-for-nothing gigolos who come home after neglecting me for so long don't get any!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get gray hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wouldn't want your awesomeness to be spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you like to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get in the mood and devour you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dick! Oh, yes! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I be your escort in the road to Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize if I've hurt your pride with economy class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First Class is 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kick ass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa, her technique is crazy-good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm a pro, I can't hold still!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice. Very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pound me harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One sheep, two sheep, three sheep,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}four worms, five worms...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And what was that water animal in Belgium?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit, he's from Hazakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get caught up in a turf war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to pocket the 100,000 yen because of the confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a Campari and soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you messed up, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it as protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the Hazakura leaders was just gunned down at a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll keep getting stronger in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should prove useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-san, why are you taking me into your confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'd like to see you survive long enough to become a real pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you're still alive, I want to make you quit your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't want me to steal your prey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, can you seduce that lady over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's top class!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't seduce her, she's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I fetch you another?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To your healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dislike hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop down and crawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick my boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make a fool out of me, you'll pay dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Hazakura boss's woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will address me as "My Queen"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a professional seducer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tables have turned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna make her crawl now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got me, Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you seduce this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The top fashion designer, Hana Morie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll call you next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it quick, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pointed me at a real psycho bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a fucking baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't figure out what kind of woman she is before you fuck her, you're not a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be a real pro, then show more discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you blame others for your lack of street smarts,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better quit being a male whore while you're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Cobra?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roppongi gigolo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can make me cum for real, I'll let you keep this car as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Cobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a sequel if you're willing to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even talk stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just never been with a woman as good as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chigasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a chance to perform the sequel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want the Cobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who the hell is this woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've attracted some bad company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's a Cobra all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda got roped into coming along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you want the sequel right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Didn't you came here on business?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but before that, make me burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, show us the goods, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna take it that far, ya might as well take off her panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Showing of in your Cobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're giving us a free peep show?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and gloat all ya want now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it all from you while you're not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucking punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome boobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who the hell I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kaitoh Jin, the boss of the Hazakura gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess up my face,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no telling what my pissed-off subordinates will do in relation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's my woman ya want, you'll have to kill me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll let it slide for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if ya don't get lost now, you'll fucking pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that scares us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've gotcha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stops here, you rotten shithead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't let that boy go,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll splatter your brains across the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, babe, put that toy away, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that cheap thing would fool us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the first shot was "playing."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to inform you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't be the first time I've filled filthy scum like you with lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I let you guys live,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no doubt you'll just give other people shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go tell your pals to stay the fuck away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from that... the hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. So you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not involved with Hazakura at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the fierce Hazakura gang boss, Kaitoh Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just a story!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get them to back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the idea of working for a gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only told them that to try and save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also outside the gang world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mizushima Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "speeding bullet" of the assassination world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I chose you only for sex, Mr. Gigolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.14,0:23:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get closer to the Hazakura boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I told you I'm not involved with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-chan, isn't your friend Suzuki a friend of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki's just my instructor as a gigolo. He helps me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Suzuki is deeply involved with Hazakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By investigating them, I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So the sequel was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.94,0:24:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we storm the boss's stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we go kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something about speeding bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no place to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.65,0:24:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why their lives burn with passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They get very hot... especially before they kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.38,0:24:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.02,0:25:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.41,0:25:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your sequel was as good as advertised.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.98,0:25:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.50,0:25:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you give up being a speeding bullet and live a happy life with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.90,0:25:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.50,0:25:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Turn on the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.65,0:25:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, the Cobra is yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.18,0:25:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.50,0:25:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it means being the target of a gang, I don't want this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you say you're not involved after all we've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.18,0:25:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come. I'll make you check out the boss's hideout for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what the boss looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the opposite. When Hazakura's goons spot me in the street, I can't get any jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.74,0:26:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem like you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.18,0:26:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you still don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.26,0:26:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, you're accompanying me to his hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.86,0:26:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, if I fail, the Cobra will need a new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.62,0:26:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.41,0:26:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm successful, I'll give you this car anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.18,0:26:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But until then you're just my chauffeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.54,0:26:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't quit, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.50,0:26:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.74,0:26:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can shoot in there with a clear mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.26,0:26:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's got me beat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.65,0:27:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've gotten myself mixed up with a crazy woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.62,0:27:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check on the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.82,0:27:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.02,0:27:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.58,0:27:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.90,0:27:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.46,0:27:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.22,0:27:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.10,0:27:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.94,0:27:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing big.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.65,0:27:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the information I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.06,0:27:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just quit already!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.58,0:27:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman like you shouldn't be doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.14,0:27:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hot woman shouldn't risk her life for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.46,0:27:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.41,0:27:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.65,0:27:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard warm words like that in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.86,0:27:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can't turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.98,0:27:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you about my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.94,0:28:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got caught up in a Hazakura dispute with the Komatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.10,0:28:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.65,0:28:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.38,0:28:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was six years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.70,0:28:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Ai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.86,0:28:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with the mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.38,0:28:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.82,0:29:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family wasn't involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.65,0:29:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just happened to be next to the Komatsu table,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.18,0:29:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they ended up full of holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.42,0:29:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the only survivor, the Komatsu boss took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.26,0:29:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day on the street, I saw the face of the man who stole my family from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.94,0:29:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was with the Hazakura, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.14,0:29:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.06,0:29:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one the cops executed was a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.58,0:29:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't let that murderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.06,0:29:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the boss who gave him the order to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.42,0:29:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.14,0:29:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.06,0:29:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I was raised apart from the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.10,0:29:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But last year, the Komatsu boss betrayed me,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.18,0:29:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I had to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.94,0:29:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate mobsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.70,0:29:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think what I did was excusable?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.54,0:30:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what it's like to have to kill the man who acted like a father to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.62,0:30:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that why you're a hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.54,0:30:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.50,0:30:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you wouldn't understand anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.30,0:30:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll take you and this Cobra to the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.02,0:30:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after that, I'm dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.94,0:30:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.62,0:30:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.58,0:30:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not at home or at the mob headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.90,0:30:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he's not at his second home in Chigasaki then he must be at his mistress's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.70,0:30:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't tell me we're gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Just take me back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.74,0:30:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what his mistress looks like, but I don't know where she lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.90,0:30:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to help me find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.54,0:30:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no obligation to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.30,0:30:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.10,0:30:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this photo of Suzuki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.26,0:30:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might know the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.50,0:30:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}do{\i0} know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.98,0:30:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do know where it is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.66,0:30:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.78,0:30:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.26,0:30:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.58,0:30:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:30:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.74,0:31:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I knew where it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.50,0:31:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't take you to such a dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.50,0:31:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.94,0:31:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use any means necessary to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.30,0:31:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's one thing I dread,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.02,0:31:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's being killed by my enemy when my target is right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.06,0:31:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to run away, then run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.66,0:31:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask for your help anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.06,0:31:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't help protect me when it really counts,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.70,0:31:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're just a smart-ass Gigolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.70,0:31:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and watch quietly as the Hazakura gang kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.62,0:31:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.26,0:31:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.90,0:31:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.78,0:31:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On one condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.10,0:31:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.18,0:31:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.78,0:32:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the mob boss is at his mistress's house right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.26,0:32:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no chance you can get out of there alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.50,0:32:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.10,0:32:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.18,0:32:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you find out where the house is, you'll have plenty of other opportunities to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no chance of getting out alive, then don't go through with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.86,0:32:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go through all this trouble to take you to your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.02,0:32:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.90,0:32:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't usually like to do this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.14,0:32:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.18,0:32:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.42,0:32:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.58,0:32:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.06,0:32:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the boss's Renz.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.18,0:33:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.18,0:33:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.78,0:33:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.18,0:33:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it okay to let Ai go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.66,0:33:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should stop her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.46,0:33:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.90,0:34:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.82,0:34:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, "speeding bullet of Komatsu."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.42,0:34:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.78,0:35:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The little bitch thinks she can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.62,0:35:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have plenty of time in Hell to regret your mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.74,0:35:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.82,0:35:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.30,0:35:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gigolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.06,0:35:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're teamed up with this stray cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.53,0:35:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stray cat? Don't you fucking call her that!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.74,0:36:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can have lots of fun in Hell together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.18,0:36:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.06,0:36:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.94,0:36:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.01,0:36:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.10,0:36:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run away, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.18,0:36:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.90,0:36:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.82,0:36:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.62,0:36:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.30,0:37:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai! Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.10,0:37:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.18,0:37:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.70,0:37:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.53,0:37:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare die!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.30,0:37:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.30,0:37:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.14,0:37:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to be all cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.70,0:37:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I couldn't keep my promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.58,0:37:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.62,0:37:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.22,0:37:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.86,0:37:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be buried at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.90,0:38:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.78,0:38:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have many precious memories of playing with my family by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.30,0:38:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai! Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.38,0:38:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to meet you before the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.53,0:38:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget that thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.30,0:38:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.06,0:38:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.42,0:38:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please kiss me... one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.62,0:38:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai. Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.66,0:38:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.22,0:38:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.26,0:41:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.30,0:41:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.50,0:41:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that fucking thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.66,0:41:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.14,0:41:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna rely on a gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.46,0:41:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.30,0:41:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you fucking gigolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.14,0:41:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.34,0:41:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it wasn't all a waste then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.50,0:41:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.18,0:41:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the anniversary of when we moved in together!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.22,0:41:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One year!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.06,0:41:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, sit down, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.53,0:42:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have the main course in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.62,0:42:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm not in the mood for that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.78,0:42:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll put you in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.90,0:42:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranko-chan's wonderful technique wows even Jin the professional gigolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.30,0:42:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.62,0:42:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You {\i1}are{\i0} in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.70,0:42:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then we're pulling an all-nighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.94,0:42:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.42,0:42:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really revive quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.98,0:42:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.14,0:42:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice!
